Verify Phone Number
---------------------------------------------------
-	Click on “YouTube Studio”  (Top right, click on profile menu)
-	Click on “YouTube Studio”
 
Click on “Settings”  (left bottom side)
 
-	Click on “Channel”
-	Click on “Feature eligibility”
-	Click on “Verify phone number”
 
-	Select “Text me the verification code”
-	Country : Bangladesh
-	What is your phone number: Your phone number type here
-	Click on “Next” button
 
-	Enter secret code from your mobile
-	Click on “SUBMIT” button
 


 



